"title": "5240: building",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5240: building",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The construction of something together with the skilled people involved. Scripture also uses the term figuratively.</p>\n<h2>Building materials</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen11:3\">GEN 11:3</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:17\">1KI 5:17</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag1:8\">HAG 1:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod27:1\">EXO 27:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:9\">1KI 6:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:3\">2CH 2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:11\">ISA 54:11</a></p>\n<h2>Building skills</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:18\">1KI 5:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod36:1\">EXO 36:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:7\">1KI 6:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs12:11\">2KI 12:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs22:5-2Kgs22:6\">2KI 22:5–22:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:1-1Chr22:2\">1CH 22:1–22:2</a></p>\n<h2>The variety of building projects</h2>\n<h3>Towns and cities</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:24\">1KI 16:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:17\">GEN 4:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg1:26\">JDG 1:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr11:8\">1CH 11:8</a></p>\n<h3>Houses</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:4\">ECC 2:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer35:8-Jer35:9\">JER 35:8–35:9</a></p>\n<h3>Temples</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:24\">ACT 17:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:2\">1KI 6:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:13\">1KI 8:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra3:10\">EZR 3:10</a></p>\n<h3>Altars</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh8:30-Josh8:31\">JOS 8:30–8:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen8:20\">GEN 8:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod24:4\">EXO 24:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam24:25\">2SA 24:25</a></p>\n<h3>Palaces</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam5:11\">2SA 5:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:1\">1KI 3:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:2\">1KI 7:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos8:14\">HOS 8:14</a></p>\n<h3>Walls</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:18\">PSA 51:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:17-Neh2:18\">NEH 2:17–2:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:11\">MIC 7:11</a></p>\n<h3>The tower of Babel</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen11:4-Gen11:5\">GEN 11:4–11:5</a></p>\n<h2>Building used figuratively</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:18\">MAT 16:18</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:1\">2CO 5:1</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:11\">1TH 5:11</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:4-1Pet2:5\">1PE 2:4–2:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:38\">1KI 11:38</a>PSA <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs118:22\">118:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:42\">MAT 21:42</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:10\">MRK 12:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:17\">LUK 20:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:11\">ACT 4:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:7\">1PE 2:7</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov9:1\">PRO 9:1</a> <em>the house of wisdom</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:24-Matt7:26\">MAT 7:24–7:26</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:48-Luke6:49\">LUK 6:48–6:49</a> <em>the wise and foolish builders</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:20\">ROM 15:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:9-1Cor3:15\">1CO 3:9–3:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor10:8\">2CO 10:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:20-Eph2:22\">EPH 2:20–2:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:12\">EPH 4:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:29\">EPH 4:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:7\">COL 2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:3-Heb3:4\">HEB 3:3–3:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:10\">HEB 11:10</a></p>",
